[quote=".Fusion, post:3, topic:14206"]Right click on compile and click edit. Replace whats in there with this [code]@echo off title CheezScape Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin/java.exe" server pause[/code] If that does not work replace the 7's with 6's.:)[/quote] :cool:
